image_analysis.description: An interior photograph of a staircase. The stairs are covered in a dark grey patterned carpet. A blue-painted metal railing with a wooden handrail follows the curve of the stairs. The walls are painted a light beige or off-white color. On the wall at the landing, there is a framed black and white photograph hanging below a circular, glowing wall-mounted light fixture. An electrical outlet is visible on the wall near the base of the stairs.
image_analysis.layout: Vertical composition showing a staircase ascending from the bottom left towards the center and right.
